Plot: A semi-paralyzed radio reporter is sent out to investigate a story that leads him into an odd subculture and on a journey of disturbing self-realization.
Title: Quid Pro Quo
Actors: Nick Stahl, Rachel Black, Jessica Hecht, Jacob Pitts
tomatoConsensus: Despite a stunning performance by Vera Farmiga, Quid Pro Quo never develops its effective parts into a convincing whole.
